      "writtenOn": "2017-09-08T19:18:03Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Is there a known scenario where this does get hit? If there isn\u0027t a known benefit then I think we should omit doing this check. If there is then I think we should convince ourselves that it wouldn\u0027t be better to catch it up stack.\n\nHow much benefit do we lose by just using the path bounds?",
      "parentUuid": "8761a868_387295a1",
      "revId": "faf66938fbec34d76d0abce126a375d22b73aa40",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
